Deep-scan each site: listings, filters, and detail pages. Confirm eligibility and deadlines on the official page.

## Before finishing an update

- Descriptions ≤ 100 words (script checks this).
- Deadlines accurate; flag verify-on-site if unclear.
- No closed or ineligible rows on Opportunities.
- Every row has a gender category.
- File saves cleanly (close other Excel locks if needed).
